IntelliMatch: AI Resume Screener

An AI-powered web app that matches candidate resumes with job descriptions using Natural Language Processing (TF-IDF) and Machine Learning.

---

Overview

IntelliMatch is a smart AI-based Resume Screening System built using Streamlit and Scikit-learn.  
It helps recruiters automatically evaluate and rank resumes based on TF-IDF similarity with a given Job Description,  
and provides an AI-powered Hire/Reject prediction.

---

Key Features

✅ Upload multiple resumes in CSV format  
✅ Paste any job description to compare  
✅ Calculates semantic similarity between resumes and job description  
✅ Predicts Hire / Reject using trained ML model  
✅ Displays Top 10 Recommended Candidates 
✅ Option to Download full results as CSV

---

Tech Stack

| Category | Technology Used |
|-----------|----------------|
| Frontend  | Streamlit |
| NLP       | TF-IDF Vectorizer (Scikit-learn) |
| Machine Learning | Random Forest Classifier |
| Storage   | CSV, Joblib |
| Language  | Python |
| Libraries | pandas, scikit-learn, joblib, streamlit |

