Installation & Setup

Step 1. Clone the Repository
git clone https://github.com/your-username/IntelliMatch-Resume-Screener.git
cd IntelliMatch-Resume-Screener

Step 2. Install Dependencies
Copy code
pip install -r requirements.txt

Step 3. Run the App
Copy code
streamlit run app/streamlit_app.py

Example Output
Candidate Name	TF-IDF Match (%)	AI Score	Decision
A. Kumar	89.4%	92	✅ Hire
R. Singh	81.7%	80	✅ Hire
M. Sharma	72.5%	64	❌ Reject


